Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是那个时候的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁
